21:05.830 --> 21:10.410
an idea at the Federal Correctional Institute in Fort Worth, where we got all

21:10.410 --> 21:14.790
these minimum security prisoners to work out some of their demons and creative

21:14.790 --> 21:15.170
writing.

21:15.810 --> 21:20.930
And the scene, the whole thing on pleasant when Gerard is in the rehab center is

21:20.930 --> 21:24.350
based on some things that we did when I was down at Fort Hood, where they had a

21:24.350 --> 21:32.470
little program for long term rehabilitation, rehabilitation patients in the

21:32.470 --> 21:35.590
hospital at Fort Hood, where they were doing some of that.

21:35.690 --> 21:37.430
And then I got to participate in a little bit of that program.

21:37.470 --> 21:38.870
And that's where the idea came from.

